				    <h1><a name="ServletInitScheduler-Initializingaschedulerwithinaservletcontainer"></a>Initializing a scheduler within a servlet container</h1>

<p><br clear="all" /></p>

<div class="code"><div class="codeHeader"><b>web.xml</b></div><div class="codeContent">
<pre class="code-java">&lt;web-app xmlns=<span class="code-quote">"..."</span>&gt;
...
	&lt;servlet&gt; 
	  &lt;servlet-name&gt;QuartzInitializer&lt;/servlet-name&gt; 
	  &lt;servlet-class&gt;org.quartz.ee.servlet.QuartzInitializerServlet&lt;/servlet-class&gt; 
	  &lt;init-param&gt;
	    &lt;param-name&gt;shutdown-on-unload&lt;/param-name&gt;
	    &lt;param-value&gt;<span class="code-keyword">true</span>&lt;/param-value&gt;
	  &lt;/init-param&gt;
	  &lt;load-on-startup&gt;2&lt;/load-on-startup&gt;
	&lt;/servlet&gt;
...
&lt;/web-app&gt;</pre>
